      "The system's objectives include maximizing threat identification, minimizing false positives, and ensuring response readiness.": {}
    },
    "A key administrator advantage is the ability to investigate inward through security layers for incident analysis.": {
      "Administrators start with perimeter monitoring to identify external threat patterns.": {},
      "They can then examine inner layers to trace potential compromises in critical systems.": {}
